subject: Merge tag 'nvme-6.1-2022-11-10' of git://git.infradead.org/nvme into block-6.1
body:

"nvme fixes for Linux 6.1

 - fix a memory leak in nvmet-auth (Sagi Grimberg)"

  nvme: quiet user passthrough command errors
